Kilmorie Primary School Early Phase Garden Party

Garden Party layout

You can enter from the 2 gates, on:

  • Kilmorie Road
  • Elsinore Road

The main building is on the Elsinore Road side but has its entrance at the end of a path from the gate on Kilmorie Road.

The playground is on the left of the path from the gate on Kilmore Road.

The Wild Garden is on the right of the path from the gate on Kilmorie Road, bordering the road.

The lawn is also on the right of the path, above The Wild Garden.

There are 2 sports areas to the right of the lawn, bordering Kilmorie Road:

  • 'The Cage', which also borders the alleyway joining Kilmorie Road to Elsinore Road
  • some courts between the lawn and 'The Cage'

The nursery building is on the left as you enter through the gate on Elsinore Road. Its playground is in front of the building as you come in.

Tickets and facilities

The Adults' WC is in the main building, on the left of the entrance.

The Kids' WC is in the main building, through the main hall, to the right of the entrance.

You can buy tickets for the magic show outside the main building, to the right of the main entrance.

You can buy raffle tickets and tokens on the stage, to the right of the path from the Kilmorie Road gate.

There are 2 seating areas:

  1. In the playground, on the left of the Kilmorie Road gate
  2. Between the Wild Garden and 'The Cage'

Games and activities

The magic show is in the main hall of the main building.

The small bouncy castle is outside the main building, on the right.

The big bouncy castle is in 'The Cage', on the side opposite Kilmorie Road.

There are games to play at 3 different places around the party:

  • games 1 and 2 are in the nursery playground, to the left of the Elsinore Road gate
  • games 3 and 4 are in 'The Cage', on the Kilmorie road side
  • game 5 is on the lawn, to the right of the path from Kilmorie Road, in front of the Wild Garden

There are lawn games on the lawn, to the right of the path from Kilmorie Road.

There is a Forest Trail in the Wild Garden.

Face painting is in front of the main building to the left of the entrance.

Food and drink

You can get food from the area between the Wild Garden and 'The Cage'.

There is a cafe between The Nursery and 'The Cage'.

A bar is on left of the path from Kilmorie Road, halfway to the main building.

There is also a sweets stall on the lawn, to the right of the path from Kilmorie Road.

Stalls

There are two stalls in 'The Cage', one for clothes and one for toys.

OlympiCubs and Magic and Mischief shows

The OlympiCubs and Magic and Mischief show times are:

  • 12.30pm
  • 1pm
  • 1.30pm
  • 2pm

Thanks!

Thank you for supporting Kilmorie! All of the money raised will of to our precious Early Years!
